{"tid":930470,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"專家警告中國可能扣押美國公司高管報復","createTime":"2018-12-06T10:37:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-06T15:29:36.000Z","uid":48083,"like":150,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":83,"replies":[{"pid":"194157dcc12dfb09e6c3978018dbb8abfd919fa0","tid":930470,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T10:37:14.000Z","msg":"專家警告稱華為CFO被捕後中國可能扣押美國公司高管<br />\nMike Murphy<br />\n2018年12月6日11:34 CST 更新<br />\n前美國商務部官員、戰略與國際問題研究中心(Center for Strategic and International Studies)現任技術政策主管James Lewis周三向媒體Axios表示，加拿大應美國政府要求逮捕中國電信設備公司華為(Huawai Technologies Co.)的一名高管後，中美緊張關係可能升級。<br />\n<br />\nLewis向Axios表示，華為是最受中國政府喜愛的企業之一，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">並警告稱&ldquo;他們將報復，中國將扣押人質。&rdquo;<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://cn.wsj.com/articles/CT-BGH-20181206110306\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcn.wsj.com%2Farticles%2FCT-BGH-20181206110306&d=to5YD4zhJeQf3P28CPo2PwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=a73b5df7\" target=\"_blank\">https://cn.wsj.com/articles/CT-BGH-20181206110306</a>"},{"pid":"31fd7ebd3be2d7e6101386fc3a1a59be3fb08273","tid":930470,"uid":163031,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T10:39:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34cadb647cc1308c2d2615c1c4f31722fc90256c","tid":930470,"uid":54824,"like":203,"dislike":0,"score":203,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T10:39:28.000Z","msg":"咪試下囉"},{"pid":"94b87c58a0f286cc6d0167eb5529805dd6af7145","tid":930470,"uid":134323,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T10:41:08.000Z","msg":"習種有咩做唔出"},{"pid":"7a6b7a13f0d68a42d3a421d844139ad76e17f9cc","tid":930470,"uid":124146,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T10:41:45.000Z","msg":"期待<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa14345fe07f4b3c73e9053989e5b2e98d631c70","tid":930470,"uid":31946,"like":57,"dislike":0,"score":57,"citedBy":